body:
Hello {{recipientName}},

A new offer is waiting for you on ORBI Shop. Shop with confidence through secure escrow, verified sellers, and a marketplace process designed to protect buyers.

Open the offer here: {{actionLink}}

Hello {{customerName}},

We have received delivery confirmation for order {{orderId}}. If everything is in order, payment will be released to the seller in line with {{businessName}} policy.

Ref: {{refId}}

Hello {{customerName}},

Your payment of {{currency}} {{amount}} for order {{orderId}} is now securely held in ORBI Escrow. The seller will be paid after delivery confirmation, in line with {{businessName}} policy.

Ref: {{refId}}

Habari {{recipientName}},

Ofa mpya inakusubiri kwenye ORBI Shop. Nunua kwa kujiamini kupitia mfumo salama wa escrow, wauzaji waliothibitishwa, na mchakato wa manunuzi unaolinda mnunuzi.

Fungua ofa hapa: {{actionLink}}

Hello {{customerName}},

Your refund of {{currency}} {{amount}} for order {{orderId}} has been processed. The time it takes for the funds to appear in your account may depend on your payment method.

Ref: {{refId}}

Habari {{customerName}},

Tumepokea uthibitisho wa kupokea bidhaa kwa oda {{orderId}}. Ikiwa kila kitu kiko sawa, malipo yataendelea kutolewa kwa muuzaji kulingana na sera za {{businessName}}.

Rejea: {{refId}}

Hello {{customerName}},

We have received your order {{orderId}} for {{currency}} {{amount}}. Once payment is confirmed, {{businessName}} will protect both buyer and seller through our secure marketplace process.

Ref: {{refId}}

Habari {{customerName}},

Malipo yako ya {{currency}} {{amount}} kwa oda {{orderId}} yamehifadhiwa salama kwenye ORBI Escrow. Muuzaji atalipwa baada ya uthibitisho wa kupokea bidhaa.

Rejea: {{refId}}

Habari {{customerName}},

Tumepokea oda yako {{orderId}} ya {{currency}} {{amount}}. Malipo yakishathibitishwa, {{businessName}} italinda mnunuzi na muuzaji kupitia mchakato wetu salama wa marketplace.

Rejea: {{refId}}

Habari {{customerName}},

Refund yako ya {{currency}} {{amount}} kwa oda {{orderId}} imechakatwa. Muda wa fedha kuonekana kwenye akaunti yako unaweza kutegemea njia ya malipo uliyotumia.

Rejea: {{refId}}
